<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>341</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nang haw, hukhing chate tho un,
 Puipa Krista belte chuh;
 Halh un, tho un, nam lopi te,
 Galma' Zion gam zuon un.

[V2]
 Pathien thu go chuh phuongzak un,
 Tuipi Vanpi gi bangin;
 Tanpa Krista thisan vangin,
 Guol chungchuong sang I chungchuong.

[V3]
 2. Mi thiengtho hangsan chieh sate,
 Ziehin ana ding det ui;
 En un, puonlap chuh a pei ui,
 Thisan zala guolzo te'n.

[V4]
 3. Thihna chuh lau talo hiel di'n,
 Krista hinna I zawm tau;
 Amah A hung kilat tiengleh,
 Ei le lopi'n lang hitiu.

[V5]
 4. A ma achun ding chiet hitiu,
 I Lal lopi mu'n he'i tiu;
 Kipaka Amah chawian in,
 Kipahman mu chiet tai tiu.</lyrics>
<title>THE SONG OF THE SOLDIERS</title>
</song>